docs/deprecated.md
   229‚Üí### Short option flag longer than a single character
   231‚ÜíShort option flags like `-ws` were never supported, but the old README did not make this clear. The README now states that short options are a single character.
   232‚Üí
   233‚Üí- README updated in Commander v3.
   234‚Üí- Deprecated from Commander v9.
   235‚Üí- Throws an exception in Commander v13. Deprecated and gone!
   236‚Üí- Replacement added in Commander v13.1 with support for dual long options, like `--ws, --workspace`.
   237‚Üí
